subject: Hello, Compliments of the day.
body:
Hello, Compliments of the day. My Name is Zhina Chun, I am a senior Staff with a public Bank 
here in Wing Hang Bank, Hong Kong
, , I am contacting you regarding a confidential business Proposal that will be of great mutual benefit to both of us ,If you are interested Kindly Contact me on my private email address for more details: 
zhinachun@gmail.com
 I look forward to hearing from you soon. Regards, Zhina Chun

subject: Re: Hello, Compliments of the day.
body:
Dear Zhina Chun,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I am intrigued by your proposal and would like to know more about it. Could you please provide more details about this business opportunity?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Barbara
